      <td width=84%><font face=Verdana size=2>Dropped High Priest again... 
      it owned, totally flawless fight.  That's not what I'm going to 
      complain about though because I love this encounter.  In my opinion 
      the HP fight is one of the best fucking fights in EQ at the moment.  
      It totally shows if you and your guild can work as separate teams for a 
      common goal.  We can!  That's not the problem.</font><p>
      <font face=Verdana size=2>The fucking problem is killing this bitch of 
      a mob (and no matter how you look at it, HP is a bitch!), going to loot 
      the corpse, and finding a caster weapon!  What the hell is this shit?  
      My guess is it was bring your daughter or son to work day and the kids 
      made up the loot for this encounter.  Now you're probably saying, 
      'Rombus you fucking stuck up uber loot whore, why are you complaining!?'  
      Here's why:<br>
 </font></p>
