      <img border=0 src=images/news/15April02/gaydagger.gif width=265 height=151></p>
      <p><font face=Verdana size=2>C'mon now, why must we plug mobs up with 
      uber^uber^ god damn caster weapons?  WHY!?  It was cool on the 
      Staff of the Silent Star in North, but the answer to making casters feel 
      all warm and snuggly on these encounters IS NOT BY PUTTING FUCKING WEAPONS 
      USABLE ONLY BY CASTERS ON THE MOBS!  If I wanted to melee and cast 
      spells I think I would have made a Ranger or a Bard... seriously, putting 
      caster weapons on uber mobs is like putting Brodie with a women, it's just 
      not right man!!!  Faldarith god the dagger, Solvan got the FT6 shield.  Grats!</font></td>
